  "title": "M & E Coordinator (A1 Builder)",
  "description": "<p>·      To oversee all works relating to mechanical and\nelectrical services such as sanitary, water, gas, lift, scv, electrical, ACMV,\netc and any other M & E installations at sites.</p><p>·      To co-ordinate all services installations to ensure\nsmooth progress and advise on matters relating to provision of openings and sizes for accurate installations.</p><p>·      To advise on building constraints with regards to the selected M&E items and recommend revisions and amendments to compatible\nto each other.</p><p>·      To take charge of the planning and production of M&E\ncoordinated shop drawings, as-built drawings and any other drawings for submission to consultants for approval.</p><p>·     To coordinate and supervise the NSC and/or subcontract M&E works for compliance to quality and time requirements.</p><p>·      To assist Project Manager in attending site meetings and briefing of M&E works.</p><p>·      To advise on statutory requirements in respect of M&E works.</p><p>·      To liaise with Consultants for any enquiry on M&E works.</p><p>·      To arrange with the subcontractors for inspections of completed M&E works including any necessary protection.</p><p>·      To check on all M&E installation prior to casting.</p><p>·      To arrange for testing of piping works prior to plastering works.</p><p>·      To prepare M&E method statements checklists and submission to consultants for approval.</p><p>·      To participate in tendering exercises in relations to M&E items and advise cost effectiveness and suitability of system.</p><p>·      To identify training needs of site staff for M & E works.<br /></p><p><u><strong>HOW TO APPLY :</strong></u></p><p>Interested candidates, please submit your resume by clicking\non <strong>“Apply Now” or aliceyap@hkmsvs.com</strong></p><p><strong>All applications will be treated in the\nstrictest confidence and only shortlisted candidates will be notified</strong></p><p>Yap Lay Choo</p><p>EA Licence No. 03C5391 | Registration No. R1987101</p>",
